disposal within their borders or that the repeal of such 
impediments was imminent to be allowed to continue sending their 
waste to south carolina 
the order affects south carolinas gsx landfill which holds 
close to a billion pounds of hazardous waste about 70 percent from 
out of state some 33 states puerto rico and the district of 
columbia used the facility in 1987 
