newspaper said it said that in that account combest said that he 
had only seen tower drunk on two or three occasions 
tower has acknowledged that he drank excessively in the 1970s 
but says he has reduced his intake to wine with dinner on sunday 
he promised to not drink a drop of alcohol if confirmed as defense 
secretary 
