speculated that the alleged smuggling operation may have gone ahead 
monday despite the arrests in atlanta because the tickets had 
already been bought 
in atlanta the illegal aliens said they paid as much as 4000 
as part of a package deal to help start a new life in new york 
of those seized at the los angeles airports terminal six 54 
were from mexico seven were from el salvador four were from 
