twoyear period when owen acted as a courier between north and 
rebels fighting the government in nicaragua 
with the issue far from settled and creating unforeseen 
implications for other classified material the judge ordered that 
the jury return wednesday morning sullivan had asked for another 
day to argue out of the jurys hearing saying im not sure what 
the rules are 
